Re Lord of the Rings movie Cc Thanks cant wait to see it Chuck wrote Unable to display image Good morning Chuck and Susan Thank you for the Austin nuts that was a fun surprise in the mail I wanted to tell you about a movie we saw yesterday in case you havent seen it yetactually Ken didnt see it because he was flying a localbut I went with a friend and we took Travis and Brandon and her two boys as well as another nice neighborhood friend of the boys We would HIGHLY recommend Lord of the Rings It was SO good Well probably go back so Ken can enjoy it sometime It was a bit violent at times but really good All of the teenagers said it was the best movie theyd ever seen It was rather long but was so suspenseful it didnt feel like wed been there very long at all Just thought Id pass that along to you in case you might want to see it over the holidays Luckily our theatre was playing it on different screens because the showing wed intended to see was sold out Luckily there was another one starting in half an hour on the other screen that wasnt sold out yetit was absolutely packed though Are youall staying at your house for Christmas or going to the cabin MERRY CHRISTMAS Love Jan Do You Yahoo Send your FREE holiday greetings online

ReHarris pictures Cc Jan Good hearing from you sounds like your Christmas is going very well glad to hear about that I am also sending you note to all to see also hope you dont mind Tell the boys and Ken Hi for us Happy New Year Chuck Susan wrote Dear Chuck Thank you so much for sending the pictures of Harris He is simply a gorgeous baby My GOODNESS hes cute What a fantastic smile too Mike and Heather will soon be entering the phase of staying up until well after midnight putting Christmas toys together for the next few years wont theysuch wonderful memories remembering the wonder and utter delight on the kids faces when theyre so young and see all the toys Santa left under the tree Christmas mornings Our boys are thrilled with their Nintendo Gamecube this year thats all they really wanted Theyve been having a great time playing it as well as computer games with their friends over here every day They havent been doing Flight Simulator much lately on the computer but seem to be enjoying The Sims still and Travis got the expansion pack for Starcraft for Christmas so they have renewed interest in that too They have friends in the neighborhood that they like to be with as much as possibleusually it seems that theyre at our house which is fine with us because theyre such nice boys Theyre all staying the night at one of the friends houses Fri night which just happens to be Kens and my th anniversary and we were planning to out for a nice dinner that night anywayso that worked out great Thanks again for sending the adorable pictures of Harris Have a nice rest of your week and HAPPY NEW YEAR in a few days Jan D D Do You Yahoo Send your FREE holiday greetings online
